        JUMP GRUNT

        Original Author(s)
          Singustromo <singustromo at disroot.org>

        Credits
          - Sounds from: https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/47266
          - Haruka (this script is roughly based off of EFT Jump and Land SFX)
          - Grinskin for the Wish :)

